Package fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.codegen

Provides the API for dynamic Java code generation using context aware generators.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Assignable
    A Java source code element that can be assigned to.
    Expression
    A Java source element that represents a value.
    Field
    Java source code element representing a class field.
    Statement
    A Java source code element that does not have a value and cannot be assigned to.
    TypedElement
    A Java source code element that has a type.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assignment
    A Java source code statement that represents the assignment of an Expression to an Assignable.
    LocalVariable
    A Java source code element that represents a local method variable.
    MapGenerator
    Code generator for Map objects.
    MethodParameterGenerator
    A generator for variables that are declared as method parameters.
    OptionalGenerator
    Generator for Optional and related types.
    SimpleField
    Implementation of Field which can represent a mutable class field.
